videos.description: Gonzaga's Johnathan Williams gets the offensive rebound and scores  the basket to get Gonzaga off to a good start.
videos.headline: Gonzaga open the game on a 7-0 run

videos.description: Gonzaga's Przemek Karnowski finds Johnathan Williams and he jams it over the defender.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Karnowski finds Williams for the dunk

videos.description: BYU's TJ Haws pulls up and drains 3-pointer from way downtown.
videos.headline: BYU's Haws makes deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Gonzaga's  Nigel Williams-Goss gets the steal and scores the layup to score their first basket of the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Williams-Goss gets the steal and the layup to open 2nd half scoring

videos.description: Gonzaga's Josh Perkins intercepts the bad pass and goes all the way and scores the basket.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Perkins gets the steal and scores the layup

videos.description: BYU's Eric Mika rises up and blocks the dunk attempt by Gonzaga.
videos.headline: BYU's Mika with the huge block at the rim to deny the dunk

videos.description: Eric Mika's basket gives BYU the lead, and Corbin Kaufusi's layup seals the Cougars' 79-71 upset victory.
videos.headline: BYU's clutch baskets puts an end to Gonzaga's perfect record

videos.description: Breaking down BYU's huge win on the road against undefeated Gonzaga and ending their perfect season.
videos.headline: Breaking down BYU's huge road upset of Gonzaga
